WEBVTT

18:55.774 --> 18:58.066
We met during the
premiere of 'Drishyam'.

18:58.149 --> 18:59.649
Oh, yeah. Now I remember.

19:00.233 --> 19:01.816
-Aren't you a psychologist?
-Yes.

19:02.566 --> 19:04.941
Actually, a friend of mine
needs help.

19:05.566 --> 19:06.733
I'll bring him.

19:07.441 --> 19:09.816
-Can I get your number?
-Of course.
